Gettrust is the first trust index on LinkedIn.

In just 3 minutes, you can get an average 23% higher response rate on your LinkedIn messages.

It's easy: just share your profile link 3 times with your contacts to get your score.

Once you've got it, just send it at the beginning of your LinkedIn messages to prove to your contacts that you're a person they can trust.

Ready to enter a world where spam and low-quality solicitations are a thing of the past?
